cc:Work.dc:title: Elvie #001
cc:Work.dc:description:
[Panel 1: Elvie is reading a copy of Linux Voice] Elvie: At last, a Linux magazine that shares my own ideals Half their profits are being ploughed back into Free Software
[Panel 2] Elvie: and the content will later be released under an open license.
[Panel 3] Elvie: its amazing what theyve managed to create using Scrib--
[Panel 4: Close up of magazine, with a note saying "Designed Using Adobe InDesign"] Elvie: Oh Never mind, I'm sure *next* year will be the year of Linux desktop publishing.
